headline.main: BREAK ENVISAGED; End of Rome Resistance in 6 Months if Terms Are Set Is Foreseen WORD TO REICH IS URGED Hull Expresses His Hope That Albanians Will Strike for Freedom From Invader BREAK ENVISAGED IN ITALIAN EFFORT

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Nov. 30 -- That Italian resistance might collapse within six months, especially if facilitated by definite announcement of the terms available to Italy, was the view expressed today in highly authorized quarters.
abstract: Collapse of Ital resistance held near; Churchill Nov 30 s on attack on Italy cited
